::DrillBit::

DrillBit saw Enfectra's missiles.
"Come on! Put some effort into it."
He shot the one missile, with an optic, blowing it away.
Useing one of his insect legs, he grabbed the other missile, turned it
around, and sent it heading back to Enfectra.
